  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.5.10">
<l>paṭanākat taṇaikkiṭantaṉ ṟavuṇar kōṉaip paṭavekuṇṭu marutiṭaippōyp paḻaṉa vēli</l>
<l>taṭamārnta kaṭalmallait talaca yaṉattut tāmaraikkaṇ tuyilamarnta talaivaṉ taṉṉai</l>
<l>kaṭamāruṅ karuṅkaḷiṟu vallāṉ velpōrk kalikaṉṟi yoliceyta viṉpap pāṭal</l>
<l>tiṭamāka vivaiyaintu maintum vallār tīviṉaiyai mutalariya vallār tāme.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who firmly master these five-and-five [verses]</l>
<l rend="indent">of the songs of delight composed of the words of Kaliyaṉ,</l>
<l>Victorious in battle, master of dark elephants in musth,</l>
<l rend="indent">[about] the ruler who rests his lotus eyes in sleep,</l>
<l>Lying on a hooded cobra bed in Talacayaṉam</l>
<l rend="indent">at Mallai by the vast, full sea, with hedged fields,</l>
<l>Having raged against the demon king so he perished,</l>
<l rend="indent">and having gone between marutu [trees],</l>
<l rend="indent">they will be able to cut their evil karma at the root.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
